Energy Label
Energy Label provides an indication of a product’s energy efficiency and can also give specific data about other relevant features of usage, such as the product’s noise emissions or water consumption. This makes it easier for consumers to save money on their household energy bills and contribute to reducing greenhouse gas emissions across the EU and UK.
